  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469280/extras/60d5d5babfc9c10a1124d7232f52455c.avif?t=1747673233\" width=600 height=149 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mushroom Picnic Party is a hand-drawn hidden object game where you help Townsfolk find all the lost little mushrooms and prepare for a picnic party!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guests from far away will attend the party, and you want to make the best impression possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469280/extras/5de88d10520ef5a16c472f432d781d9b.poster.avif?t=1747673233\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469280/extras/5de88d10520ef5a16c472f432d781d9b.webm?t=1747673233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469280/extras/8f6cf35748a5159a548fd4f21d078883.avif?t=1747673233\" width=600 height=189 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of little mushrooms to find!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creative puzzles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets to find out</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy and wholesome vibes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13 locations to explore</p></li></ul>",
